name: Alotta Tribute - by MM
description:
There really isn't sufficient words to describe what Alotta meant to our culture and community. To lose one so kind and talented has hit us all so hard. But we do what we can to remember him, we make art. 

This is my tribute to the man, the myth, the legend ᗩᒪᎧTTᗩ ᗰᎧᑎEY❂
